content: I had my training today and then tried to make a few calls.  Ran into some snags.  Would like to try again, but can someone invite me to a practice room please?
Hi Carol, we will be doing something on the stage real soon! I'll send over a link to join when that gets started

Thanks so much!  Will this give me an opportunity to practice or otherwise view all elements of the script?  I thought I had done so until I was in the middle of a call and felt lost.  It came out ok, I think, but I had promised to send him a link and then couldn't figure out how to do it.  Bummed!
Head over there now they're going to go through training and can answer questions! https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1242802529222398022
